\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The Independent Institute of Education \'28IIE\'29 is a Private Higher Education Institution registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training and has programmes accredited by the CHE. \line \line The Institution is currently applying for the accreditation of Diploma in Human Resource Management Practice which will be offered in the contact mode of delivery at the following sites\'3A\line \line 1. IIE Rosebank College Polokwane - Polokwane \line 2. IIE Rosebank College\'2C Braamfontein Mega - Braamfontein\'2C Johannesburg \line 3. IIE Rosebank College - Durban - Durban \line 4. IIE Rosebank College - Bloemfontein - Bloemfontein \line 5. IIE Rosebank College - Pietermaritzburg\'2C - Pietermaritzburg \line 6. IIE Rosebank College\'2C Pretoria - Pretoria \line \line \line The IIE is accredited to offer the following programmes in the field of Human Resources\'3A \line - Higher Certificate in Human Resource Practices \line - Diploma in Human Resource Management Practice \line \line The Institution is going through a re-accreditation cycle.\line \cell \pard 

